# API base URL, inlined into the web bundle at BUILD time (Expo EXPO_PUBLIC_* vars are static).
# - Web dev server (npm run web):  http://localhost:8080   (absolute; cross-origin, CORS-covered)
# - Expo Go on a device:           http://<your-LAN-IP>:8080
# - Prod / full-stack Docker image: leave EMPTY — the Spring image serves this bundle AND the
#   API on one origin (ADR-008), so calls go to a relative /api. The Dockerfile sets it to "".
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
